### Public Battery View
# View battery status by public hash
# No authentication required - anyone with the hash can view

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8081
@publicHash = 00f5e48a2ac0a5eb25b821a4595c28d8

### View Public Battery
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/battery/public/{{publicHash}}

